  <description>
[STL]Satellite Inc Wolfein Race ver 0.2.2

This mod adds the Satellite Inc Wolfein Race, a variant of the Wolfein Race.
We plan to add another variant, the Comet Inc Wolfein Race, in the future.

They belong to the unique factions Satellite Inc and Comet Inc, specific to this mod.

They are armed with equipment added by the Satellite Inc Mod.
We also plan to create a Comet Inc Mod.

*Note: Remember that the equipment from the Satellite Inc Mod is overpowered in a vanilla environment.

Mod Installation Order:
Harmony
Core
DLCs
Humanoid Alien Races
Ancot Library
Wolfein Race
Wolfein Race Gene Patch
Astrallium Core
[STL] Satellite Inc Mod
  </description>
